Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Work is over for now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally I can live here again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,About this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Luis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,1031 has no empty room left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The room I used to live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Neil lives there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember there was a room beside it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damao lives there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lynn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about letting Luis sleep on the sofa like last night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok for one night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But long term is unacceptable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What about living in the fridge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His body could be stored separately
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fridge is for food only
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It also protects against moisture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he actually living
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Abu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too small for you to live with me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, my room is pretty big
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never seen Abu's room before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and have a look
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've listened to the cards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandpa I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, wrong door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You even had a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put your coffin here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Abu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Luis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I don't need that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so inconvenient to live together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ok, Luis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much bother for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't need that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you insist for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you be polite about such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone broke into our house
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luis is right
